data.description: Adorable 2BR/1BA home minutes from Highway 321. Welcoming front porch. Home features newer roof and HVAC (2016 per previous owner), newer replacement windows, laminate flooring throughout in 2020, fresh interior paint throughout in 2020. Solid birch cabinets in kitchen. Side door entry into laundry/mud room. Refrigerator, washer and dryer to remain. Large, level lot with plenty of space. Storage shed and detached carport. Cajah Mtn. Road is on the DOT plans for improvement/widening.
